<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>古风游戏说明</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;700&family=ZCOOL+KuaiLe&display=swap');

body {
background-color: #EAE0C8;
font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
color: #3D2B1F;
line-height: 2;
padding: 20px;
}

.scroll-container {
max-width: 800px;
margin: 40px auto;
background-color: #FDFBF5;
border: 2px solid #C8B090;
box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
padding: 40px 50px;
border-radius: 5px;
position: relative;
}

.scroll-container::before,
.scroll-container::after {
content: '';
position: absolute;
left: 0;
right: 0;
height: 25px;
background: #C8B090;
border: 2px solid #A48865;
}

.scroll-container::before {
top: -27px;
border-bottom: none;
border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
}

.scroll-container::after {
bottom: -27px;
border-top: none;
border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
}

h3 {
font-family: 'ZCOOL KuaiLe', cursive;
color: #8B0000;
text-align: center;
font-size: 2.2em;
margin-bottom: 15px;
padding-bottom: 10px;
border-bottom: 2px solid #D3B89E;
letter-spacing: 3px;
}

.version-section {
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.version-info {
font-size: 0.9em;
color: #5a4a3e;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
}

.tooltip-container {
position: relative;
display: inline-block;
margin-left: 8px;
cursor: pointer;
}

.tooltip-btn {
background-color: #8B0000;
color: white;
border-radius: 50%;
width: 20px;
height: 20px;
font-size: 14px;
line-height: 20px;
font-weight: bold;
text-align: center;
font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
}

.tooltip-text {
visibility: hidden;
width: 280px;
background-color: #3D2B1F;
color: #FDFBF5;
text-align: left;
border-radius: 6px;
padding: 10px 15px;
position: absolute;
z-index: 1;
bottom: 150%;
left: 50%;
margin-left: -140px;
opacity: 0;
transition: opacity 0.3s;
line-height: 1.6;
font-size: 0.95em;
}

.tooltip-text::after {
content: "";
position: absolute;
top: 100%;
left: 50%;
margin-left: -5px;
border-width: 5px;
border-style: solid;
border-color: #3D2B1F transparent transparent transparent;
}

.tooltip-container:hover .tooltip-text,
.tooltip-container:active .tooltip-text {
visibility: visible;
opacity: 1;
}

.important-notice {
color: #006400;
background-color: #f0fff0;
border: 1px solid #90ee90;
font-weight: 700;
padding: 8px 15px;
margin-top: 15px;
border-radius: 5px;
font-size: 1.05em;
}

ol {
list-style-type: none;
padding-left: 20px;
counter-reset: item-counter;
}

li {
margin-bottom: 1.5em;
counter-increment: item-counter;
position: relative;
padding-left: 35px;
}

li::before {
content: counter(item-counter, cjk-ideographic) "、";
color: #8B0000;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 1.2em;
position: absolute;
left: 0;
top: -3px;
}

strong {
font-weight: 700;
color: #C00000;
font-style: normal;
}

.warning-icon {
color: #D9534F;
font-weight: bold;
font-size: 1.2em;
}

.note-box {
background-color: #F5EFE4;
border: 1px dashed #D3B89E;
padding: 15px 20px;
margin: 25px 0;
border-radius: 4px;
}

.final-section {
text-align: center;
margin-top: 40px;
padding-top: 20px;
border-top: 1px solid #D3B89E;
}

.final-section p {
margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.cta-button {
display: inline-block;
background-color: #8B0000;
color: #FDFBF5;
padding: 12px 30px;
text-decoration: none;
font-family: 'ZCOOL KuaiLe', cursive;
font-size: 1.3em;
border-radius: 5px;
border: 2px solid #610000;
box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #610000;
transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
position: relative;
top: 0;
}

.cta-button:hover {
background-color: #A11a1a;
top: 2px;
box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #610000;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scroll-container">
<h3>游玩前准备</h3>

<div class="version-section">
<div class="version-info">
当前版本为v10.2
<div class="tooltip-container">
<div class="tooltip-btn">!</div>
<span class="tooltip-text">v10.2-修复了一些10.1的bug，修复了创意工坊更新的问题</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="important-notice">
请仔细阅读下方说明，不然出现问题不予理睬，本卡只免费发布在类脑以及我的个人频道，如果出现在其他地方，均为盗用！
</div>
</div>

<ol>
<li>请关闭预设的小剧场，卡内有专门玩小剧场的地方</strong></li>
<li>如果右滑卡顿请关闭其他的所有正则只保留角色卡的正则</strong></li>
<li>如果你以前玩过这张卡并更新了新版，请<strong>务必确认</strong>是否已单独进行<strong>【删除世界书】</strong>的操作。如果没有，<strong>请先删除世界书再导入新卡！</strong></li>
<li>创建存档后，你需要在游戏设置内<strong>导入预设的正则</strong>。<br><strong>注意：</strong><strong>不要导入</strong>任何会隐藏正文的正则（例如“小总结”这类只发送总结的正则）。</li>
<li><span class="warning-icon">⚠️</span> <strong>请务必查看游戏的设置中每一项内容！必须查看！！！</strong><br>如果发现手机端<strong>点不到设置或显示不全</strong>，请在手机浏览器设置中调整<strong>【浏览器缩放】</strong>。</li>
<li>请<strong>关掉【表格插件】</strong>，它可能会引起未知问题。</li>
</ol>

<h3>常见问题解答 (FAQ)</h3>
<p>这里整合了许多人常遇到的问题，<strong>请务必阅读</strong>。如果仍有疑问或想找好玩的DLC，欢迎加入我的频道询问。</p>

<div class="note-box">
<strong>不知道用什么预设和正则？</strong><br>
进我的频道，里面有分享默认的预设和正则文件。
</div>

<ol>
<li><strong>一定要单独删除世界书再更新角色卡</strong>，否则你的游戏尾部可能会出现一串看起来像<strong>变量</strong>的内容。</li>
<li><strong>一定不要导入</strong>任何<strong>【消除正文】、【小总结替换】、【只保留摘要/小总结】</strong>等类型的正则。</li>
<li>本卡自带<strong>超强记忆系统（分段记忆）</strong>，配合变量系统可大幅减少token消耗。请在设置中打开<strong>【分段记忆】</strong>，并将 X 设置为 <strong>5-7</strong>，Y 设置为 <strong>20-30</strong>，这是最佳配置。</li>
<li>游玩如果碰到<strong>【存档无法创建】</strong>的问题，请去相关帖子查看<strong>云存档</strong>的解决方法。</li>
<li><strong>玩的开心！看完说明向右滑倒即可开始游戏！只要你按照我的要求进行设置，这将会是你玩过最爽的卡，没有之一！</strong></li>
</ol>

<div class="final-section">
<p>如果你想玩到我写的其他超高质量的角色卡，可以加入我的频道，并且还会有许多<br>二创作者制的凡人修仙传的拓展内容供你添加<br>这里放一份我的 Discord 频道链接：https://discord.gg/DdUnPKM7Dq</p>
<a href="https://discord.gg/DdUnPKM7Dq" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-button">点击前往【LP的小窝】</a>
</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
